About Me

Welcome to my place. It all started years ago when I started to enjoy reading. I slowly started recognising changing accents and narration styles in different books. Slowly I strted to nurture my intrest of writing something. But I kept everything I wrote to myself. When I shared with some friends about my intrest, they encouraged me. A friends gave me my first diary and encouraged me to take it further. Thats when I took a step ahead, thanks to my friend.
